14
00:00:38,583 --> 00:00:40,375
PRINCE WU IS LEADING
AN EVACUATION EFFORT

15
00:00:40,417 --> 00:00:43,333
WHILE ASAMI AND VARRICK ARE
CREATING FLYING MECHA-SUITS.

16
00:00:43,375 --> 00:00:45,458
